|YKOInvasions can happen regularly on Darkwind.  They are announced by a 
siren [DIPPS] and involve regular messages broadcast to the players.

During invasions, NPCs and shops in town are regular targets, and 
the shops may be destroyed.  It takes some time to repair the shops
and get them working again, and they may not be usable in the meantime.

Lower level players are advised to stay out of the city of Darkwind
during an invasion, as players may be targetted by powerful mobs
roaming through town.

A siren [DIPPS] will signal the all-clear when the invaders have been
vanquished or succeed in their invasion.
